{"tid":592793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BBC] 英國將驅逐23名俄羅斯外交官","createTime":"2018-03-14T13:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T16:32:40.000Z","uid":56015,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b98de39298978a0959edd5481b4f6e12e78e580c","tid":592793,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"首相文翠珊稱，在莫斯科拒絕解釋俄羅斯前特工於Salisbury 被俄製神經製劑襲擊之後，英國將驅逐23名俄羅斯外交官。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊稱，該等外交官是被認為&ldquo;未申報的情報官員&rdquo;，他們將會有一個星期離開。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯否認參與企圖謀殺前特工Sergei Skripal和他的女兒尤莉婭的。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊為此案定下的午夜十二點前期限, 而俄方拒絕合作。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-43402506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-43402506&d=8aBMm4NG%2BqopGMwwVxN5qGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5916fe8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-43402506</a><br />\n<br />\n英文原文: <br />\n<br />\nThe UK will expel 23 Russian diplomats after Moscow refused to explain how a Russian-made nerve agent was used on former spy in Salisbury, the PM says.<br />\n<br />\nTheresa May said the diplomats, who have a week to leave, were identified as &quot;undeclared intelligence officers&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nRussia denies being involved in the attempted murder of former spy Sergei Skripal and his daughter Yulia.<br />\n<br />\nIt refused to meet Mrs May's midnight deadline to co-operate in the case."},{"pid":"24139f39b7937a138be8fef5452f4fed25c6963b","tid":592793,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0b2909d14920b19128ed313def2e2a1cc317d4","tid":592793,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"又開始劃分勢力了"},{"pid":"744781dd0b3616a7a03b4a6f432ec2da6461f9e6","tid":592793,"uid":56015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":